banner.presentation1: Hello! I am an Argentine full stack developer, oriented to web development and university student. Enthusiastic about new technologies and knowledge.

about.title: Programming student and certified full stack web
about.content: I am a professional with a positive and motivated attitude, always willing to learn and improve in my work. I consider me self-taught, dedicated with passion and tenacity to each project in which I am involved, thereby allows me to meet quality objectives and delivery times.

service.scrumD: Working in multidisciplinary teams, participating in the design of sprints, definition of user stories, task estimation, progress monitoring and feedback.
service.design: Design, development and maintenance of web applications

work.try: I try to work focusing on the aesthetics of my pages and their best utilities
